{"tid":2224982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《幻愛》導演: 《佔領立法會》獲金馬獎提名, 更令我振奮！","createTime":"2020-10-01T03:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:49:18.000Z","uid":134071,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1fcf35264da948a14e872356bd8295f3dd1106ac","tid":2224982,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈電影《佔領立法會》, 《幻愛》, 《夜更》榮獲台灣金馬獎多項提名.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2224150/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2224150/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(《夜更》導演郭臻就係《十年&bull;浮瓜》的導演,&nbsp;講述一名的士司機見證反送中示威.&nbsp;&nbsp;)<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>《幻愛》導演周冠威則指：「這是我第一個編寫的劇本，第一稿完成於2006年，輾轉十幾年時間，最終得到肯定，非常感恩，多謝曾俊榮與我合作編寫。同時也喜聞以香港民主抗爭為內容的《佔領立法會》及《夜更》入圍，我們能夠代表香港，充滿感概，他們獲得關注，更令我振奮！」曾俊榮則指：「首次創作長篇劇本而能夠入圍金馬提名實在意想不到！非常鼓舞！」</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201001/CHA2AR2OXVHEDGSG5YUTL62DZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201001%2FCHA2AR2OXVHEDGSG5YUTL62DZQ%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kygwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=38489a23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201001%2FCHA2AR2OXVHEDGSG5YUTL62DZQ%2F&h=978aa0b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201001/CHA2AR2OXVHEDGSG5YUTL62DZQ/</a>"},{"pid":"7225739c376611d33b788c647a63189ac1ebeefe","tid":2224982,"uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"《迷航》都係香港導演拍嘅，講當年中國烏坎村爭取民主嘅事.&nbsp;&nbsp;此片都獲金馬獎最佳紀錄片提名."},{"pid":"038ee875046d5982b106341d3a29039173759bfe","tid":2224982,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"黃圈手足互撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513ae1f7c8af782d5130a8b23ae0b566fd428097","tid":2224982,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime